  "texts": [
    "Instead of investing time on reading and memorizing scientific literature updates and guidelines, ChatGPT can provide a viable alternative.",
    "Indeed, a recent systematic review examined the potential applications of Language Model models (LLMs) in healthcare education.",
    "The review highlighted several benefits of ChatGPT in healthcare education, such as enhanced personalized learning experiences and an emphasis on critical thinking and problembased learning.",
    "25 To determine to what extent ChatGPT could provide accurate responses and reliable information, further research is needed to validate the efficacy of ChatGPT in providing accurate answers in the medical domain, specifically in the context of VR.",
    "Furthermore, studies should be conducted to determine if ChatGPT's performance can be enhanced through techniques such as question repetition and integration of reliable medical literature to ChatGPT."
  ]
}